(7, 1, '2019-02-13 14:02:30', '2019-02-13 16:02:30', '<div class=\"cols\">\r\n<div class=\"col2\">[text* nome class:icone-nome placeholder \"Nome\"]\r\n<div class=\"col2\">[email* email class:icone-email placeholder \"Email\"]\r\n<div class=\"col2\">[text* cidade class:icone-cidade placeholder \"Cidade\"]\r\n<div class=\"col2\">[text* pais class:icone-pais placeholder \"País\"]\r\n<div class=\"col2\">[text* redesocial class:icone-redesocial placeholder \"Rede social\"]\r\n<div class=\"col2\">[text* website class:icone-website placeholder \"Website\"]\r\n<div class=\"col2\">[tel* telefone class:icone-telefone placeholder \"Telefone\"]\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col2\">[text* assunto class:icone-assunto placeholder \"Assunto\"]\r\n<div class=\"col1\">[textarea mensagem class:icone-mensagem placeholder \"Mensagem\"]\r\n<div class=\"col1\">[submit \"Enviar mensagem\"]\r\n\n1\nContato site\natendimentosomadev@gmail.com\natendimentosomadev@gmail.com\n<strong>Nome:</strong> [nome]\r\n<strong>Email:</strong> [email]\r\n<strong>Assunto:</strong> [assunto]\r\n<strong>Mensagem:</strong> [mensagem]\nReply-To: [email]\n\n1\n\n\nSOMADev \"[your-subject]\"\nSOMADev <wordpress@192.168.1.36>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on SOMADev (http://localhost/~djalmatoledo/recrutamento)\nReply-To: atendimentosomadev@gmail.com\n\n\n\nMensagem enviada com sucesso!\nUm ou mais erros ocorreram!\nUm ou mais erros ocorreram! Tente novamente!\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nObrigatório\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.', 'contato-pt', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'contact-form-1', '', '', '2019-04-01 09:51:47', '2019-04-01 12:51:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost/~djalmatoledo/recrutamento/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=7', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
